    - http://www.meetup.com/phillyphp/events/39806022/
    - SPAs Single Web page Applications
    - Client-side MVC's
    - Search a book for MVC model
    - State of browser
        - Explore if use director.js to enable the state of maqinato
        - Seems better option Backbone.js to tath

Classes
    - Use the Revealing Module Pattern to desing "classes"
    - Use Singleton for Database classes (http://desarrolladorsenior.blogspot.com/2009/09/el-patron-de-diseno-singleton-esta.html)
    - Use Data Abstraction Layer
